name: Deli’s Kitchen - Japan Grill Delicacy

reviews.text: 1st time ordering from ‘em and the Hakata Black Curry options do not disappoint. Balanced (sweet, tangy, savoury) curry that we can eat a tub of with moist, succulent proteins. A bit pricey me thinks but quality of cook is well worth it.
